Novice Panel Missions

■Perform a limit break 3 times on a realized 5★ EX weapon and enhance it to max
Strategy Tip:
• They can be obtained from draws and by trading in ten EX power tokens at the EX power token exchange.
*The EX power tokens, book of Ruin's mysteries, and Ruin's adamantine ingots needed to clear this mission can be obtained by clearing the mission "Clear Act 1, Ch. 1, 'Primus Island.'"
 • 5★ EX weapons are those with an initial rarity of 5★ and an initial CP of 70 that grant the use of EX abilities.
